    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，APB_RTC作为顶层模块。那内部第一层结构怎么划分？我看到有APB Slave接口、配置寄存器，还有核心逻辑？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APB Slave",
        "rtc_config_regs",
