    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，第一层放APB Slave接口，然后是一个rtc_config_regs模块处理配置，还有一个rtc_regs是用PeakRDL生成的寄存器组。这三个并列。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APB",
        "CFG",
        "REGS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，APB、CFG、REGS三个模块。rtc_regs我标注一下PeakRDL来源。接下来核心逻辑要单独包一层吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "REGS",
        "CORE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，核心逻辑单独做一个子图叫rtc_core，里面包含时间计数器、闹钟比较器、中断产生器和BCD逻辑四个模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CORE",
        "Time Counter",
        "Alarm Comparator",
        "Interrupt Generator",
        "BCD Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "rtc_core子图已创建，内部四个模块：Time Counter、Alarm Comparator、Interrupt Generator、BCD Logic。现在画外部连接？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CORE",
        "TIME",
        "ALARM",
        "INT_GEN",
        "BCD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "外部APB Bus连到APB Slave，APB Slave输出CFG信号到rtc_config_regs，rtc_config_regs再连到rtc_regs，rtc_regs最后连到rtc_core。这是一条配置通路。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BUS",
        "APB",
        "CFG",
        "REGS",
        "CORE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "配置通路：BUS - APB - CFG - REGS - CORE，四层串联。rtc_core还需要时钟输入吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CLK",
        "CORE"
